description: This file is a C header file defining internal API prototypes for the Http Ato Status object within a BroadWay service system. It declares functions related to creating status code and name tables, and retrieving status codes and names.

methods.name: HttpAtoStatusCreateCodeTable
methods.description: Creates a table of status codes.

methods.name: HttpAtoStatusCreateNameTable
methods.description: Creates a table of status names.

methods.name: HttpAtoStatusGetAtomCode
methods.description: Retrieves the status code corresponding to a given name.

methods.name: HttpAtoStatusGetAtomName
methods.description: Retrieves the status name corresponding to a given code.
